        <updateDate>2015-06-04T20:53:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Advancing Growth in the Economy through Distilled Spirits Act or the AGED Spirits Act</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude the aging period from the production period for distilled spirits for purposes of determining whether a taxpayer can expense, rather than capitalize, interest costs paid or incurred during the production period.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
